troy the chip )\n\n Circular Kyr'Ozch Chip Mold 253155\nAdds 150 Nano Init \n<img src=rdb://130740>\n\n Square Kyr'Ozch Chip Mold 253157\nAdds 3% Damage\n<img src=rdb://130842>\n\n Triangular Kyr'Ozch Chip Mold 253159\nAdds -5% Nano Cost\n<img src=rdb://130745>\n\nComments\n\nNice improvements for the NT Cyberdeck. An already-uber item.\n"), array(56,"Jobe Armor Tier 2","\nIngredients\n\na piece of Jobe Armor Tier 1 Click here /tell {myname} recipe 58 for recipe\n<img src=rdb://213586>\n\n Consanguineal Embryo of Yomi'Arallu 239836\n<img src=rdb://144705>\n\n Canister Of Pure Liquid Notum 223446\n<img src=rdb://100305>\n\na special Advent x 3\n( ie : Advent of the Industrious 239475 )\n<img src=rdb://136597>\n\na Will x 3 \n( ie Will of The Reposeful 239469 )\n<img src=rdb://151031>\n\nFirst\n\nUpgrade your Jobe Armor Tier 1 up to lvl 160. Some jobe Armor part doesn't exist in Tier 1 form, but you can upgrade them to QL 160 using a Joker's Glyph 227905 on it.\n\nGo to jobe and give the Consanguineal Embryo of Yomi'Arallu and the Three Will to your Profession IPS, he will give you a Red Glyph ( ie Red Glyph of Enel 218342 ).\n\nThen, give him the 3 Advents, he will you a Glyph ( ie Horned Black Glyph of Shere 218347 ).\n\nRecipe\n\nCanister Of Pure Liquid Notum\n+\nRed Glyph\n=\n<img src=rdb://227529>\nRed Glyph - Awakened\n( ie Red Glyph of Aban - Awakened 227625 )\nSkills: | QP |\n\n\nRed Glyph - Awakened\n+\nGlyph\n=\n<img src=rdb://227567>\nProfession Red Glyph\n( ie Red Glyph of the Lovers 227795 )\nSkills: | PS |\n\n\nProfession Red Glyph\n+\na piece of Jobe Armor Tier 1\n=\n<img src=rdb://213586>\na part of Jobe Armor Tier 2\n( ie Second Tier Doctor Suit Pants 214755 )\nSkills: | PS |\n\nDetails\n\nAdventurer\n Will of the Reposefull 239469\n<img src=rdb://151031>\n Advent of the Prudent 239478\n<img src=rdb://136593>\n\nAgent\n Will of the Tempestuous 239470\n<img src=rdb://151033>\n Advent of the Impetuous 239480\n<img src=rdb://25796>\n\nBureaucrat\n Will o