will revert to an empty container and also spawn:\n\n Data Receptacle 160978\n<img src=rdb://287621>\n\nClick the Data Receptacle on a Grid Terminal and you will be granted access to the Fixer Grid."), array(633,"Infused Viral Compiler","\nIngredients \n\n All parts required for this process can be found in Albtraum. \nYou will need to build an Ancient Engineering Device as well if you do not have one already. \nA link to this tradeskill process is included\n\n Dormant Ancient Circuit 267794\n<img src=rdb://158233>\n\n Viral Compiler 251223\n<img src=rdb://119132>\n\n Ancient Engineering Device 267751\n<img src=rdb://156095>\nNote:To build your Ancient Engineering Device, go here: \n Ancient Engineering Device /tell {myname} recipe 594\n\nRecipe \n\nAncient Engineering Device\n+\nDormant Ancient Circuit\n=\n<img src=rdb://158233>\n Active Ancient Circuit 267795\nSkills: | 1500 ME |\n\nActive Ancient Circuit\n+\nViral Compiler\n=\n<img src=rdb://119132>\n Infused Viral Compiler 267913\nSkills: | 6X QL in ME |"), array(690,"Spirit Infused Yutto's Modified NCU","\nIngredients \n\n These nifty new NCU will be a great upgrade for your yuttos NCU. You can find the parts in Albtraum. You can find the guide for the tool needed here /tell {myname} recipe 594. \n\n Ancient Engineering Device 267751\n<img src=rdb://156095>\n\n Dormant Ancient Circuit 267794\n<img src=rdb://158233>\n\n Yuttos Modified NCU 238921\n<img src=rdb://205500>\n\nRecipe \n\nAncient Engineering Device\n+\nDormant Ancient Circuit\n=\n<img src=rdb://158233>\n Active Ancient Circuit 267795\nSkills: | 1500 ME | \n\nActive Ancient Circuit\n+\nYuttos Modified NCU\n=\n<img src=rdb://205500>\n Spirit Infused Yuttos Modified NCU 267797\nSkills: | 6X the QL of ME | \n\nTo make a QL 220 NCU into a QL 300 you will need 1800ME."), array(691,"Masterpiece Ancient Manual Aiming Aid","\nIngredients \n\n All parts required for this process can be found in Albtraum.\n\n Empty Ancient Device 267709\n<img src=rdb://218753>\