ient Scrap of Spirit Technical Knowledge 267681\nSkills: | 1875 NP |\n\nImproved Ancient Manual Aiming Aid\n+\nAncient Scrap of Spirit Technical Knowledge\n=\n<img src=rdb://218778>\n Masterpiece Ancient Manual Aiming Aid 267707\nSkills: | 1250 CL |"), array(692,"NCU Memories","\nIngredients \n\n The Legacy of Xan NCU memories come in 4 different sorts and can be upgraded 6 times.\n\n Base NCU - Type 00 (0/6) 277436\n<img src=rdb://276942>\n\n NCU Memory Cell 277182 x 6\n<img src=rdb://276923>\nor\n Intelligence Memory Cell 277170 x 6\n<img src=rdb://276921>\nor\n Biological Metamorphosis Memory Cell 277831 x 6\n<img src=rdb://276920>\nor\n 1-Hand Blunt Memory Cell 277904 x 6 \n<img src=rdb://276922>\n\nRecipe \n\n\n<highlight>NCU Memory NCU<end>\n\nNote:NCU Memory exclusively buffs your NCU.\nAt QL300 it will buff a massive 192 NCU with 6 Memory Cells added to it. \n\nBase NCU - Type 00 (0/6)\n+\nNCU Memory Cell\n=\n<img src=rdb://276936>\n Memory NCU (1/6) 278757\nSkills: | Requires QLx1.5 EE QLx1.5 NP QLx4.5 CL|\n\nRepeat 5 times for:\n Memory NCU (6/6) 278782\n<img src=rdb://276941>\n\n<highlight>Abilities NCU<end>\n\nNote:Abilities NCU can buff all your base abilities by up to 5 per NCU.\nIt can include one cell of each ability \n\nBase NCU - Type 00 (0/6)\n+\nIntelligence Memory Cell\n=\n<img src=rdb://276924>\n Abilities NCU - Type 02 (1/6) 277051\nSkills: | Requires QLx1.5 EE QLx1.5 NP QLx4.5 CL|\n\nRepeat 5 times for:\n Abilities NCU - Type 3F (6/6) 277166\n<img src=rdb://276929>\n\n<highlight>Nano NCU<end>\n\nNote:Nano NCUs can buff all six nano skills at the same time by up to 5 per NCU.\nIt can only include one cell of each ability \n\nBase NCU - Type 00 (0/6)\n+\nBiological Metamorphosis Memory Cell\n=\n<img src=rdb://276943>\n Nano NCU - Type 01 (1/6) 277506\nSkills: | Requires QLx1.5 EE QLx1.5 NP QLx4.5 CL|\n\nRepeat 5 times for:\n Nano NCU - Type 3F (6/6) 277823\n<img src=rdb://276918>\n\n<highlight>Weapons NCU<end>\n\nNote:Abilities NCU can buff all your base abilities by up to 5 per NCU.\nIt can include one cell of each ability \n\nBase NCU - Type 00 (0/6)\n+\n1-Hand Blunt Memory Cell\n=\n<img src=rdb://276930>\n 1-Hand Blunt Skill NCU (1/6) 278314\nSkills: | Requires QLx1.5 EE QLx1.5 NP QLx4.5 CL|\n\nRepeat 5 times for:\n 1-Hand Blunt Skill NCU (6/6) 278339\n<img src=rdb://276935>"), array(693,"Professional Stellar Nanodeck","\nIngredients \n\n Most of these items can only be acquired if you have access to Mitaar Hero, Ground Chief Vortexx and the 12-Man encounters,\nas well as a few key items from various high-level encounters/quests bits! \n\n Unknown Mixture 281095\n<img src=rdb://281093>\n\n A piece of cloth 281098\n<img src=rdb://281096>\n\n Nanodeck Activation Device 280785\n<img src=rdb://280784>\n\n Kenneth's Polishing Gel 255555\n<img src=rdb://156504>\n\n xxx Nanodeck 270762\n<img src=rdb://270749>\n\n Star of xxx 244691\n<img src=rdb://131260>\n\nRecipe \n\nNote: for demonstration purposes we'll show how to build MA nanodeck:\n\nUnknown Mixture\n+\nKenneth's Polishing Gel\n=\n<img src=rdb://281092>\n Grostad's Polishing Gel 281094\n\nGrostad's Polishing Gel\n+\nA piece of cloth\n=\n<img src=rdb://281097>\n Grostad's piece of polishing cloth 281099\n\nGrostad's piece of polishing cloth\n+\nStar of Equanimity\n=\n<img src=rdb://281044>\n Stellar Equanimity 281046\n\nNanodeck Activation Device\n+\nMartial-Artist Nanodeck\n=\n<img src=rdb://281042>\n Activated Martial-Artist Nanodeck 280764\n\nStellar Equanimity\n+\nActivated Martial-Artist Nanodeck\n=\n<img src=rdb://281043>\n Stellar Martial-Artist Nanodeck 280778\n"), array(694,"Masterpiece Ancient Combat Tuner","\nIngredients \n\n All parts required for this process can be found in Albtraum.\nThe tuners at each phase are NO DROP, so make sure you have enough Computer Literacy for those bits! \n\n Empty Ancient Device 267709\n<img src=rdb://218753>\n\n Ancient Scrap of Spirit Knowledge 267677 x 4\n<img src=rdb://163575>\n\n Ancient Scrap of Saturated Spirit Knowledge 267679 x 4\n<img src=rdb://163575>\n\n Crystalised Memories of a Technician 267698\n<img src=rdb://72770>\n\n Crystalised Memories of a Mechanic 267701\n<img src=rdb://72771>\n\n Crystalised Memories of an Instructor 267710\n<img src=rdb://72771>\n\n Crystalised Memories of a Sniper 267704\n<img src=rdb://72771>\n\n Crystalised Memories of a Warrior 267697\n<img src=rdb://72771>\n\nRecipe \n\n<highlight>Ancient Combat Tuner<end>\n\nEmpty Ancient Device\n+\nCrystalised Memories of an Instructor\n=\n<img src=rdb://218765>\n Ancient Combat Tuner 267678\nSkills: | 1250 CL |\n\n<highlight>Enhanced Ancient Combat Tuner<end>\n\nAncient Scrap of Spirit Knowledge\n+\nAncient Scrap of Saturated Spirit Knowledge\n=\n<img src=rdb://163575>\n Ancient Scrap of Condensed Spirit Knowledge 267680\nSkills: | 1750 PT |\n\nAncient Combat Tuner\n+\nAncient Scrap of Condensed Spirit Knowledge\n=\n<img src=rdb://218766>\n Enhanced Ancient Combat Tuner 267656\nSkills: | 1250 CL |\n\n<highlight>Advanced Ancient Combat Tuner<end>\n\nAncient Scrap of Spirit Knowledge\n+\nAncient Scrap of Saturated Spirit Knowledge\n=\n<img src=rdb://163575>\n Ancient Scrap of Condensed Spirit Knowledge 267680\nSkills: | 1750 PT |\n\nEnhanced Ancient Combat Tuner\n+\nAncient Scrap of Condensed Spirit Knowledge\n=\n<img src=rdb://218767>\n Advanced Ancient Combat Tuner 267682\nSkills: | 1250 CL |\n\n<highlight>Superior Ancient Combat Tuner<end>\n\nAncient Scrap of Spirit Knowledge\n+\nAncient Scrap of Saturated Spirit Knowledge\n=\n<img src=rdb://163575>\n Ancient Scrap of Condensed Spirit Knowledge 267680\nSkills: | 1750 PT |\n\nCrystalised Memories of a Sniper\n+\nCrystalised Memories of a Warrior\n=\n<img src=rdb://72769>\n Combined Crystalised Combat Memories 267705\nSkills: | 1250 NP |\n\nCombined Crystalised Combat Memories\n+\nAncient Scrap of Condensed Spirit Knowledge\n=\n<img src=rdb://163575>\n Ancient Scrap of Spirit Combat Knowledge 267681\nSkills: | 1250 CL |\n\nAdvanced Ancient Combat Tuner\n+\nAncient Scrap of Spirit Combat Knowledge\n=\n<img src=rdb://218768>\n Superior Ancient Combat Tuner 267695\nSkills: | 1250 CL |\n\n<highlight>Masterpiece Ancient Combat Tuner<end>\n\nAncient Scrap of Spirit Knowledge\n+\nAncient Scrap of Saturated Spirit Knowledge\n=\n<img src=rdb://163575>\n Ancient Scrap of Condensed Spirit Knowledge 267680\nSkills: | 1750 PT |\n\nCrystalised Memories of a Technician\n+\nCrystalised Memories of a Mechanic\n=\n<img src=rdb://72769>\n Combined Crystalised Technical Memories 267702\nSkills: | 1875 NP |\n\nCombined Crystalised Technical Memories\n+\nAncient Scrap of Condensed Spirit Knowledge\n=\n<img src=rdb://163575>\n Ancient Scrap of Spirit Technical Knowledge 267681\nSkills: | 1875 NP |\n\nSuperior Ancient Combat Tuner\n+\nAncient Scrap of Spirit Technical Knowledge\n=\n<img src=rdb://218764>\n Masterpiece Ancient Combat Tuner 267696\nSkills: | 1250 CL |"), array(695,"Player City Building Guide","\nInfo\n\n You can not buy ready-made houses. You have to build them using tradeskills.\nThe store where all this is sold is Uncle Bazzit's Shop in Meetmedere (MMD).\nThere are two types of buildings: advanced and regular ones. To make an advanced building you need to upgrade you Regular Building Structure 254807.\nThe QL of the building ranges from 1-300 and is determined by Generic Organic Immunity System 254822. \nUncle Bazzit only sells up to QL75. To find out how to make a higher QL, look further down in this guide.\nAdvanced structures: Headquarter, Market, Guard House\nRegular Structures: Grid House, Notum Mining Operations, Notum Silo, Landing Pad, Satellite Uplink, ECM Tower, Swimming Pool, Sidewalk Cafe, Sky Bar\n\nIngredients\n\n Generic Volatile Nanobots 247760\n<img src=rdb://156482>\n\n HSR Compressed Regenerating Bioplate 202540\n<img src=rdb://203584>\n\n Blueprint - Regular Building Structure 247768\n<img src=rdb://247770>\n\n Floorplan - Clan Swimming Pool 255481\n<img src=rdb://121435>\n\n Generic Organic Immunity System 254822\n<img src=rdb://100334>\n\n\nNote:for a building of QL75+ you will need to build your own\nGeneric Organic Immunity System and will also need:\n\n Kyr'Ozch Structural Analyzer 247100\n<img src=rdb://247097>\n\n Solid Clump of Kyr'Ozch Bio-Material 254804\n<img src=rdb://247101>\n\n Advanced Bio-Comminutor 154332\n<img src=rdb://149951>\n\n Manteze Scout Nasal Membrane 247762\n<img src=rdb://247761>\n\n\n\nNote:for advanced buildings you will also need:\n\n Fertilized Giant Chirop Egg 247788\n<img src=rdb://20405>\n\n Slow-Killing Poison 247791\n<img src=rdb://100335>\n\n Unrefined Notum Salt 247786\n<img src=rdb://247785>\n\n Uncle Bazzit's Bio-Mechanical AI 247794\n<img src=rdb://247793>\n\nRecipe\n\n<highlight>Generic Organic Immunity System<end>\n\nNote: To make a QL75+ building, regular or advanced, you need a Solid Clump of Kyr'Ozch Bio-Material 254804 and a Manteze Scout Nasal Membrane 247762.\nThe QL of the Clump of Bio-Material sets the QL of the Generic Organic Immunity System (and the building).\n\nKyr'Ozch Structural Analyzer\n+\nSolid Clump of Kyr'Ozch Bio-Material\n=\n<img src=rdb://292809> \n Kyr'Ozch Viral Serum 254805\nSkills: | 4.5 x QL EE |\nNote: Refining a clump of bio material does not guarantee viral serum as a result.\nThey can turn into several different items.\n\nAdvanced Bio-Comminutor\n+\nManteze Scout Nasal Membrane\n=\n<img src=rdb://99236> \n Membrane Pulp 247763\nSkills: | 400 PH |\n\nMembrane Pulp\n+\nKyr'Ozch Viral Serum\n=\n<img src=rdb://100334> \n Generic Organic Immunity System 254822\nSkills: | 3.5 x QL PH |\n\n<highlight>Regular Building<end>\n\nGeneric Volatile Nanobots\n+\nHSR Compressed Regenerating Bioplate\n=\n<img src=rdb://247756> \n Strong Regenerating Bioplate 247757\nSkills: | 4x QL CH |\n\nStrong Regenerating Bioplate\n+\nGeneric Organic Immunity System\n=\n<img src=rdb://247769> \n Superior Bioplate 254806\nSkills: | 400 PH |\n\nBlueprint - Regular Building Structure\n+\nSuperior Bioplate\n=\n<img src=rdb://256071> \n Regular Building Structure 254807\nSkills: | 4 x QL ME |\nNote: for advanced structures, skip the next step\n\nRegular Building Structure\n+\nFloorplan - Clan Swimming Pool\n=\n<img src=rdb://255802> \n Clan Swimming Pool 254164\nSkills: | 5 x CL |\n\n<highlight>Advanced Buildings<end>\n\nUnrefined Notum Salt\n+\nFertilized Giant Chirop Egg\n=\n<img src=rdb://20405> \n Mutating Giant Chirop Egg 247789\nSkills: | 400 PH |\n\nSlow-Killing Poison\n+\nMutating Giant Chirop Egg\n=\n<img src=rdb://20405> \n Poisoned Giant Chirop Egg 247790\nSkills: | 400 CH |\n\nAdvanced Bio-Comminutor\n+\nPoisoned Giant Chirop Egg\n=\n<img src=rdb://99239> \n Mutating Bio-Pulp 247792\nSkills: | 400 PH |\n\nUncle Bazzit's Bio-Mechanical AI\n+\nMutating Bio-Pulp\n=\n<img src=rdb://247793> \n Bio-Mechanical Computer 247795\nSkills: | 400 QFT |\n\nBio-Mechanical Computer\n+\nRegular Building Structure\n=\n<img src=rdb://256070> \n Superior Building Structure 254829\nSkills: | 4 x QL ME |\n\nFloorplan - Clan Large Organization Headquarters\n+\nSuperior Building Structure\n=\n<img src=rdb://255788> \n Large Clan Organization Headquarters 254200\nSkills: | 5 x QL CL |\n\n<highlight>Alternative way of making Strong Regenerating Bioplate<end>\n\n Neutron Displacer 149823\n+\n Stalker Carapace 247817\n=\n<img src=rdb://247754> \n Non-Regenerating Bioplate 247755\n\n Advanced Bio-Comminutor 154332\n+\n Rollerrat Queen Blood 247758\n=\n<img src=rdb://100330>\n Rollerrat Queen Erythrocyte 247759\n\nRollerrat Queen Erythrocyte\n+\nNon-Regenerating Bioplate\n=\n<img src=rdb://247756>\n Strong Regenerating Bioplate 247757\n"), array(696,"Transmographic Dimension Shifter","\nIngredients \n\n Dr. Ness (from the Arid Rift quest) has a very nice tool for you after you've built a Ness' Decoy Device for him. The tool will warp you out of whatever place in Arid Rift back to the Unicorn staging area\n\n Semi Working Cellular Assembler 275464\n<img src=rdb://205510>\n\n Insulated 