ion Ring\n=\n<img src=rdb://281195>\n Sniper's Signet of The Apocalypse 281194\n\nComments\n\nEach ring gives you a profession specific buff when activated."), array(698,"Trimmer - Improved Actuators","\nIngredients \n\nThis Trimmer will heal your pet for up to 6k of HP and will give an additional boost to damage for 600 secs.\nIt will lock your Mechanical Engineering skill for 60 minutes.\n\n Trimmer Casing 263824\n<img src=rdb://154935>\n\n Smelly Liquid 253173\n<img src=rdb://20412>\n\nRecipe \n\nSmelly Liquid\n+\nTrimmer Casing\n=\n<img src=rdb://292754>\n Trimmer - Improve Actuators 253189\nSkills: | trimmer casing needs to be 90% of the Smelly Liquid |\n"), array(699,"Subspace Storage Device","\nIngredients \n\n Two-Dimensional Hole 245718\n<img src=rdb://203551>\n\n Subspace Mesh 245720\n<img src=rdb://205520>\n\n Meta-Cerebellum Ring 245722\n<img src=rdb://151933>\n\n Short Circuited Spiritech Circlet 245728\n<img src=rdb://245726>\n\n Short Circuited Spiritech Circlet 245729\n<img src=rdb://245727>\n\nRecipe \n\nTwo-Dimensional Hole\n+\nSubspace Mesh\n=\n<img src=rdb://203551>\n Subspace Pocket 245719\nSkills: | 1125 Psychology |\n\nSubspace Pocket\n+\nMeta-Cerebellum Ring\n=\n<img src=rdb://203551>\n Subspace Meta-Cerebellum Pocket 245721\nSkills: | 1125 QFP |\n\nShort Circuited Spiritech Circlet\n+\nShort Circuited Spiritech Circlet\n=\n<img src=rdb://151922>\n Stabilized Spiritech Circlet 245730\nSkills: | 1125 EE |\n\nSubspace Meta-Cerebellum Pocket\n+\nStabilized Spiritech Circlet\n=\n<img src=rdb://203551>\n Subspace Storage Device 245723\nSkills: | 1125 QFP |"), array(700,"Galactic Jewel","\nIngredients \n\n Frozen Crystal Compound drops from Cascading Molokh, Novictum Blight and Reprogrammed Mezzorash in Alappaa.\nWhile all the Compounds looks almost the same there are really several types that drop. Easiest way to check which one dropped is to open the tradeskill window and check the result.\n\n Frozen Crystal Compound 269800\n<img src=rdb://269799