93642\nor \n- | | <img src=rdb://291371> + <img src=rdb://292758> = <img src=rdb://291371> | SSC Bastion Right Shoulder Armor - Fatou 293651 + Mandelbrot Upgrade Plate 292536 = SSC Bastion Right Shoulder Armor - Mandelbrot 293649\nStep 11. \n- | | <img src=rdb://291379> + <img src=rdb://292782> = <img src=rdb://291379> | SSC Bastion Back Armor - Mandelbrot 293633 + Collatz Upgrade Plate 292537 = SSC Bastion Back Armor - Collatz 292194\nor \n- | | <img src=rdb://293723> + <img src=rdb://292782> = <img src=rdb://293723> | SSC Bastion Left Shoulder Armor - Mandelbrot 293642 + Collatz Upgrade Plate 292537 = SSC Bastion Left Shoulder Armor - Collatz 291932\nor \n- | | <img src=rdb://291371> + <img src=rdb://292782> = <img src=rdb://291371> | SSC Bastion Right Shoulder Armor - Mandelbrot 293649 + Collatz Upgrade Plate 292537 = SSC Bastion Right Shoulder Armor - Collatz 291931\n<yellow>\nNo tradeskills required.Not sure =)\n<end>"), array(799,"Pyramid Of Home","Awakened update for 5k Tokenboard : Laughing Spirit Capsule (Boss 1) + Crying Spirit Capsule (Boss 2) + Screaming Spirit Capsule (Boss 3) = Primed Spirit Capsule\n\nAwakened update for Beast Armor (Boots / Pants / Gloves / Sleeves) :\nInert Sigil of Alighieri + Portable Notum Infusion Device (reusable tool) = Charged Sigil of Alighieri\n\nAwakened update for Beast Armor (Neck / Burden / Shoulder / Head / Chest) :\nInert Sigil of Machiavelli + Portable Notum Infusion Device (reusable tool) = Charged Sigil of Machiavelli")
